description:
Beautiful, passionate, one of a kind, breathtaking, smart… 
Wait a minute... She wrote this about herself!

Nina is a trickster and a fraud. Once a powerful agent of Heaven, THE Keeper and bestower of luck - this Fox spirit went rogue and purposely upset the delicate balance of the world by giving out too much luck (and money!)
Cast down to earth and stripped away from most of her capabilities, she gets a chance at a slow redemption by … being a beacon of luck for humanity?

Oh for crying out loud!
What is this? A slice of life comedy?!
